Navy is elegant and timeless. Muted metallic sequins dazzle in an understated way. Mix it up with mismatched bridesmaid styles, or keep things simple with one dream dress for all of your lovelies. Make holiday magic this season in a festive look that will land you at the top of the best-dressed guest list. Sparkle in a silver sequin mini dress, amp up a cozy black sweater with metallic pants, or dazzle in ultra-glittery extras like rhinestone boots, belts, and hair clips. Winter whites are hotter than ever for holiday, so whether you're headed to a family gathering or a New Year's Eve bash, you've got plenty of en-blanc options like a leopard print puff-sleeve dress, satin one-shoulder frock, shimmery sequin top, or knee-high boots. Feel free to add un-basic black into the mix, too. Keep it cocktail-chic in a strapless black and white sheath, opt for an upgraded LBD with sheer sleeves, or dial up the drama by adding tall black boots to a printed daytime dress (office party, anyone?).
